title.62: The Mutant Misadventures of Cloak and Dagger (1988) #12

description.1: Thor and Hercules are summoned to the Black Galaxy, where they must wage war to survive!
description.5: A Human Torch solo story! Who are the musterious Seekers, and what do they want with Johnny Storm? Guest-starring Rusty Collins, the fire-powered mutant from X-Factor!
description.6: Banshee, Jean, and Forge continue their mission in the Morlock Tunnels. Forge is having flashbacks about his service in Vietnam. All this, while trying to save Peter Nicholas and Callisto from Masque.
description.11: At the mercy of Magneto!? What has caused the Scarlet Witch to break bad?
description.12: What if the Fantastic Four had lost the Trial of Galactus? With Reed Richards sentenced to death, can the remaining members of the FF stop a galactic alliance from destroying Earth?
description.16: The Avengers run into trouble in international waters after they are intercepted by Russia's People's Protectorate. Shortly after this interference, the Avengers are surprised by an Atlantean army led by Tyrak, Meranno, and Orka!
description.17: Cap tackles drug pushers in the first battle in a drug war that will blow Manhattan wide open!
description.18: Alex gains a new ability... but is it more a curse than a blessing? Meanwhile, Franklin Richards tries to locate Galactus.
description.23: The Rev and Jigsaw are in cahoots to turn Frank Castle's life into a living hell.
description.24: Conan and Jorrma risk everything to stop an army from destroying Jorrma's village.
description.27: The Darkhold has been opened! The vampires have completed their rite! VARNAE is reborn -- the first Lord of Vampires!
description.28: The saga in Hawaii comes to a close when Frank Castle and Microchip finally face off against a little girl's captors!
description.29: Daredevil continues his endeavor to escape Hell, and all hope seems lost. But his plight is seen by a voyager of the stars - THE SILVER SURFER!
description.34: Another day, another alternate dimension! This time around, Excalibur must face off with this dimension's Magik, and then throw down with the super-team known as the Justicers! Plus - a shocking death you'll have to see to believe!
description.35: After Hulk saves Doctor Strange, the Sorcerer Supreme creates a mystical portal within Banner's mind- allowing Bruce to speak directly to the Hulk!
description.36: Iron Man in a showdown with Samurai Steel!
description.38: Thor's old foe Ulik joins forces with the Wrecking Crew!
description.42: Even with the Black Celestial defeated, Galactus is still on course to devour the entire universe! Can the FF manage to stop him in time before all of existence is destroyed?
description.43: Banshee and Forge perform a rescue mission to save an unconscious Jean Grey in the Morlock Tunnels. After Jean is safely reunited with her teammates, she makes a shocking discovery about the remaining X-team on Muir Isle.
description.48: The first appearance of Lifeform! Who is this bestial, ever-evolving foe, and why is the Punisher dead set on killing him?
description.49: Corsair and his Starjammers head to Earth! The full potential of Phalkon is revealed, while Deathbird readies for battle with her Imperial Guard in tow. X-Factor and Excalibur guest-star!
description.50: Lifeform separates the Hulk and Bruce Banner, pitting the two halves against each other! Could the Hulk really end up killing Bruce?
description.52: What if Captain Marvel had not died? In one of the most tragic stories of the Marvel Universe, Mar-Vell sucumbed to the cancerous Black End. But in this universe, he's cured…but what happens when he unknowingly passes that sickness to Earth and other worlds, causing a galactic plague?
description.55: If Styx and Stone don't break Spidey's bones, Venom will!
description.56: Nebula achieves godlike power via the Infinity Union! That's bad news for the Stranger and Avengers, who are trapped in the madwoman's reign of terror. Will Nebula's hubris lead to her downfall?
description.57: Cap finally goes on a date with Diamondback, but Gamecock, the Trump, Black Mamba, Asp, and Anaconda want to make it a night they won't forget! Plus a special Diamondback tale!
description.59: Will the savage, gray She-Hulk be unleashed? And if so, will even her greatest allies be able to stop her?
description.63: The Punisher outfits himself in a mech suit to level the playing field against the Reavers!
description.65: The young Conan must survive the first in a series of grueling Cimmerian rituals designed to make him a man!
description.66: The war for the Darkhold continues! But the vampires have discovered how to use the Darkhold, and summon a dangerous new foe to destroy Doctor Strange!
description.67: When a little girl is kidnapped and taken hostage by Hawaiian drug dealers, the Punisher and Microchip unite to pull off a rescue mission.
description.69: TRAPPED IN HELL! Mephisto has ensnared Daredevil and his friends, where they must each face their greatest inner challenges!
description.72: Excalibur's adventures on a parallel Earth continue! The Hellfire Club puts their plan for domination into effect, and Excalibur must race against time to stop them! But nothing can prepare them for when they come face to face with the Hellfire Club's shocking leader - Iron Man!?
description.73: The Hulk comes face-to-face with the Freedom Force, a group of villains demanding his detainment. But a lot more is on the line than even Banner is aware.
description.74: Things go haywire when Tony Stark visits an old abandoned Stark space station. Things get even worse when A.I.M. technology sends the station hurtling towards Earth!
description.75: Thor and Hercules combine their strength the combat The Dweller!
description.79: The Fantastic Four, Iron Man, Thor, and Gladiator face off against the Black Celestial! The fate of the future comes down to this final confrontation!
description.80: In a Madripoor restaurant, Wolverine, Psylocke and Jubilee are attacked by Harry Malone's Harriers, who have taken on a commission to abduct Wolverine. With their friend gone, Psylocke and Jubilee, despite their mutual dislike, figure out a plan to find and rescue Wolverine.
description.86: What if Professor X became the Juggernaut? Behold an earth where Charles Xavier finds the Crimson Gem of Cyttorak and turns into the unstoppable Juggernaut! When a twist of fate leads mutants to be persecuted worse than ever, this Xavier's dream of the future becomes one of mutant supremacy! Who can stop this Juggernaut?
description.88: She-Hulk and Howard the Duck's adventure in the Baloney-verse continues! But when bitten by a horde of angry demons, Shulkie becomes a mindless, smashing killing machine — just like her cousin, the Hulk!
description.91: Microchip and the Punisher are in grave danger when the Reavers, cyborg enemies of the X-Men, attack their warehouse!
description.92: Witness the birth of Conan— and the battle that destroyed his village!
description.93: Power Pack comes face-to-face with a herald of Galactus... and the Devourer of Worlds himself!
description.94: Star trippin' with the Starjammers! Joined by Professor X and Lilandra, Corsair helms his team on a cosmic quest to find the fabled planet Phalkon. But usurping Shi'ar Empress Deathbird lies in wait, and she's ready for WAR!
description.95: Venom is back! There's only one man in town that's happy to see the symbiote-wearing villain in town and that man is Jonathan Caesar. But why?
description.96: The Stranger sets his sights on Nebula's Infinity Union device. Determined to prevent the Stranger, the Avengers race to find the Infinity Union before it falls into wrong hands. Plus, newbie Spider-Man makes a mistake that costs his teammates dearly.
description.97: The Red Skull escapes from the prison Magneto put him in. And now the Red Skull and Crossbones and the Skeleton Crew are out for revenge!
description.99: Our heroes find Ahura, the son of Black Bolt -- and he’s being targeted by an angry mob!

7.text: A man who taught Wolverine peace is dead. Now, it's his killers who have a lesson waiting!

9.text: The Silver Surfer finds himself pitted against the formidable Algol Demonstar in an arena duel for a huge alien audience.

13.text: Quasar's chariot awaits! The crowd cheers on as Quasar bears a sword to fight gladiator-style. But, when an unsuspected adversary enters the ring, Quasar may be forced to face the one opponent he cannot defeat...

15.text: The Kingpin is scouring New York for a powerful biotoxin that could kill millions. Ghost Rider must prevent him from obtaining the poison at all costs! Plus, Ghost Rider versus Blackout!

20.text: More mutliversal madness with She-Hulk…and her reluctant sidekick Howard the Duck!

21.text: Namor and Namorita try to rub elbows with society’s elite…too bad an explosion in a nearby bay interrupts their festivities!

22.text: Will Moon Knight be able to free himself of his mercenary past, or will it overwhelm him?

25.text: Witness the creation of a new Deathlok! Will he be a hero or a villain?

26.text: The Guardians versus The Stark and Taserface- a battle that’s out of this world! Also featuring Firelord! Plus: Starhawk and Aleta split up (but don't they share the same body)!?

27.text: The Darkhold has been opened! The vampires have completed their rite! VARNAE is reborn -- the first Lord of Vampires!

28.text: The saga in Hawaii comes to a close when Frank Castle and Microchip finally face off against a little girl's captors!

29.text: Daredevil continues his endeavor to escape Hell, and all hope seems lost. But his plight is seen by a voyager of the stars - THE SILVER SURFER!

30.text: Cable takes the New Mutants under his wing! It's time for a new HQ, new uniforms, and a whole new way of doing business!

32.text: The Hydra Affair Part 1.  Is Madame Hydra the bait for a plot to kill Nick Fury?

39.text: The hired guns appear to have succeeded in bringing down Spider-Man, but will the Chameleon true to his word?

40.text: Mesmero and Infectia attempt to ensnare Beast through Vera Cantor.

44.text: Wolverine's debt to a mobster turns into an adventure in babysitting! While waiting for assassins, he tells the tale of the boy raised by wolverines!

46.text: Ghost Rider versus the Cypress Pool Jokers!  Plus, how is Danny Ketch adjusting to becoming the new Ghost Rider?

47.text: Welcome to the Marvel Universe of the 31st Century! The Guardians of the Galaxy, Protectors of the Cosmos, begin their mission to find Captain America’s shield!

51.text: Having been dumped from their outer space battle with Magneto, the West Coast team finds itself caught in an earthquake which may have unnatural causes.

53.text: Modred is back -- and wants Chton free! Quasar and Excalibur may be able to defeat him, but Modred may have them fooled like never before…

54.text: Silver Surfer and Mantis combine forces in “The Great Terror”, an alternate universe tale! The Kree Intelligencia is after Mantis’ human/plant hybrid son, Sprout! Digital issue omits "The Believer" story.

58.text: The saga of the LIFEFORM continues! New York City becomes the prey for the Lifeform, and only Daredevil stands in its way!

59.text: Will the savage, gray She-Hulk be unleashed? And if so, will even her greatest allies be able to stop her?

60.text: Namorita guest-stars! Namor traces the Griffin back to the company that hired him…Roxxon Industries!

61.text: Moon Knight is hunted and put on trial for crimes committed during his mercenary days. Guest-starring Paladin, Sandman, and the Wild Pack.

62.text: Is this the issue where Dagger finally gets her sight back? Read on and find out!

64.text: The Surfer tries to take his revenge on Garnok, but will it alleviate his guilt over the people he failed to save from Galactus?

66.text: The war for the Darkhold continues! But the vampires have discovered how to use the Darkhold, and summon a dangerous new foe to destroy Doctor Strange!

67.text: When a little girl is kidnapped and taken hostage by Hawaiian drug dealers, the Punisher and Microchip unite to pull off a rescue mission.

68.text: When Fury arrives in Scotland, a terrifying threat emerges from the skies!

69.text: TRAPPED IN HELL! Mephisto has ensnared Daredevil and his friends, where they must each face their greatest inner challenges!

70.text: It's Cable versus Freedom Force! Does Cable know the whereabouts of Skids and Rusty?

76.text: The Chameleon assembles Spider-Man's foes from Acts of Vengeance and hires them to put an end to the Wall-Crawler!

81.text: There's a new villain in Madripoor, and Wolverine's looking for a fight - but how can he see what he's gotten into if he's snow-blind? The Snow Queen strikes!

84.text: Danny Ketch is the Ghost Rider, the Spirit of Vengeance! His adventures through hellfire and vengeance start here!
Danny Ketch is the Ghost Rider, the Spirit of Vengeance! His adventures through hellfire and vengeance start here!

85.text: Talk about trouble - the Avengers are up past their necks in problems! Magneto makes his big move! The Scarlet Witch turns traitor! And just whose side is Quicksilver on? Also ... did Tigra kill - and eat - Dr. Pym?

87.text: Dr. Minerva and Atlas are at it again! Will they finally be able to capture Quasar? Or will Dr. Minerva and Atlas take a one-way Kree Starcruiser back to Kree space?

88.text: She-Hulk and Howard the Duck's adventure in the Baloney-verse continues! But when bitten by a horde of angry demons, Shulkie becomes a mindless, smashing killing machine — just like her cousin, the Hulk!

89.text: Even Caleb and Carrie Alexander can’t help Namor take on his newest foe…the power-mad Griffin!

90.text: Moon Knight against the Bushman! Don't miss this epic battle!

98.text:
"THE CHAOS SERPENT PART 4 Leviathan cannot succeed- his victory could usher in World War III! Captain America joins the fray in the final chapter of the Chaos Serpent!
"

99.text: Our heroes find Ahura, the son of Black Bolt -- and he’s being targeted by an angry mob!
